        <updateDate>2021-06-14T11:00:58Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Renewable Chemicals Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill allows a new tax credit for the production of renewable chemicals. Specifically, it allows a credit for up to 15% of the sales price of each pound of a renewable chemical. A <i>renewable chemical </i>is any chemical that is produced in the United States from renewable biomass and is not less than 95% biobased content.</p> <p>The bill also allows a 30% tax credit for investment in renewable chemical production facilities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
